<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>World Car Unveiling Event</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #343a40;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #343a40;
            color: white;
            padding: 2rem 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #6c757d;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #6c757d;
            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .lead {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .featurette {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .featurette img {
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

        .featurette img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #343a40;
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <%- include('partials/navbar1') %>

  

    <main class="container py-5">
        <section>
            <h2 class="section-title">Event Overview</h2>
            <p class="lead">The World Car Unveiling Event is a premier automotive showcase, where manufacturers from around the globe reveal their latest models, innovations, and cutting-edge technology. This year, the event takes place in [Location], attracting car enthusiasts, industry professionals, and media from all over the world. Attendees can expect an exciting lineup of new vehicles, expert panels, and immersive experiences that highlight the future of mobility.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="section-title">Key Highlights</h2>
            <p class="lead">This year's event promises to be groundbreaking, featuring some of the most anticipated cars in the automotive industry. Here are a few key highlights:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Electric Vehicles:</strong> Major manufacturers are unveiling their latest electric models, pushing the boundaries of sustainability and performance.</li>
                <li><strong>Autonomous Driving Technology:</strong> Companies are showcasing advancements in autonomous driving systems, making strides towards safer and more efficient transportation.</li>
                <li><strong>Smart Connectivity:</strong> Vehicles equipped with the latest connectivity features, integrating seamlessly with smart devices and offering enhanced user experiences.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="section-title">Featured Cars</h2>
            <div class="row featurette">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h3 class="featurette-heading">1. The Future EV: Model X</h3>
                    <p class="lead">The Model X represents the pinnacle of electric vehicle technology. With a range of over 400 miles, ultra-fast charging capabilities, and a spacious, luxurious interior, this vehicle sets a new standard for electric SUVs.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <img src="static/ev1.avif" alt="Future EV Model X" class="img-fluid">
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row featurette">
                <div class="col-md-6 order-md-2">
                    <h3 class="featurette-heading">2. The Luxury Sedan: Model S</h3>
                    <p class="lead">The Model S redefines luxury in the automotive world. With its elegant design, state-of-the-art technology, and unmatched performance, it offers a driving experience like no other. Equipped with advanced safety features and an intuitive infotainment system, it caters to the most discerning customers.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
                    <img src="static/sed1.avif" alt="Luxury Sedan Model S" class="img-fluid">
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row featurette">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h3 class="featurette-heading">3. Rivian R1T (2024)</h3>
                    <p class="lead">Rivian's R1T is an all-electric pickup truck, known for its off-road capabilities, innovative design, and range of around 314 miles. It combines ruggedness with high-tech features, catering to adventurers and eco-conscious drivers alike..</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <img src="static/riv1.avif" alt="Compact Car Model C" class="img-fluid">
                </div>
            </div>


            
            <div class="row featurette">
                <div class="col-md-6 order-md-2">
                    <h3 class="featurette-heading">4.Ford Mustang Mach-E (2024)</h3>
                    <p class="lead">A fully electric SUV inspired by the iconic Mustang, the Mach-E blends performance and practicality. It offers a range of up to 312 miles and features a sporty design, making it a popular choice for those wanting electric performance in an SUV form..</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
                    <img src="static/for1.jpg" alt="Luxury Sedan Model S" class="img-fluid">
                </div>
            </div>



            <div class="row featurette">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h3 class="featurette-heading">5.Lucid Air (2024)</h3>
                    <p class="lead">Lucid Motors' Air sedan is a competitor to Tesla's Model S, with a focus on luxury and technology. It offers an impressive range of up to 516 miles on a single charge and combines high performance with a plush interior.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <img src="static/lu1.webp" alt="Compact Car Model C" class="img-fluid">
                </div>
            </div>



            <div class="row featurette">
                <div class="col-md-6 order-md-2">
                    <h3 class="featurette-heading">6.Mercedes-Benz EQS (2024)</h3>
                    <p class="lead">The EQS is Mercedes' flagship electric sedan, offering luxury and cutting-edge technology. It has a range of around 350 miles, a high-tech interior with an expansive digital dashboard, and impressive aerodynamics for efficiency.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
                    <img src="static/mer12.webp" alt="Luxury Sedan Model S" class="img-fluid">
                </div>
            </div>

            
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="section-title">Innovations in Automotive Technology</h2>
            <p class="lead">This year's unveiling features several groundbreaking technologies that are shaping the future of the automotive industry:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Battery Technology:</strong> New advancements in battery technology are leading to faster charging times and increased range for electric vehicles.</li>
                <li><strong>Artificial Intelligence:</strong> AI is revolutionizing how cars interact with drivers, providing personalized experiences and enhancing safety features.</li>
                <li><strong>Augmented Reality:</strong> AR is being integrated into head-up displays, offering real-time navigation and safety alerts without distracting the driver.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="section-title">Expert Panel Discussions</h2>
            <p class="lead">Throughout the event, industry experts will engage in panel discussions covering various topics, including:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Future Trends in Electric Mobility</li>
                <li>The Role of Technology in Enhancing Road Safety</li>
                <li>Global Market Insights and Consumer Preferences</li>
                <li>Sustainability Practices in Automobile Manufacturing</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

       
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer1') %>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
